{"id":"1507331","title":"Roadmap","lastModified":"2011-05-15 20:18","lastModifiedBy":"sinegar","content":"Essence of Confluence roadmap:\n * v1.0 (May 15, 2011)\n ** Limited to favourite pages\n ** Offline content (5MB limit)\n ** Minimal Wiki syntax support\n ** Infrastructure (API, build process, website, promotional material)\n * v2.0\n ** Space browser (for favourite spaces)\n ** Activity list\n ** Improved Wiki syntax support (or Confluence 4.0 data format support)\n ** Improved locale storage\n ** Code cleanup\n * v3.0\n ** Create content (comments and activities)\n ** ? (driven by user feedback)"}